# Implementation Plan - Replicate zeffdakilla.neocities.org Layout

I will replicate the layout of `https://zeffdakilla.neocities.org/` using HTML and CSS. The layout is a classic fixed-width (600px) centered design with a sidebar and main content area, typical of early 2000s web design.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> I will use generated placeholder images for the background textures and header to match the "retro" vibe, as I cannot directly copy the copyrighted assets from the original site.

